# BondMaster Development Rules
Version: 1.0
Framework: Next.js 15+ (App Router)
Language: TypeScript
Hosting: Vercel
Backend: Supabase PostgreSQL
UI: Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui

---

# Development Rules

- Never remove completed functionality.
- Mark completed items with `[X]`.
- Mark incomplete items with `[ ]`.
- Build one module at a time.
- Every feature must include:
  - UI
  - Database
  - Validation
  - API / Server Actions
  - Permissions
  - Audit Logging
  - Responsive Design
- Never break existing APIs.
- All database operations use Server Actions.
- Validate all forms with Zod.
- Every table supports:
  - Pagination
  - Search
  - Sorting
  - Filtering
  - CSV Export
- Every record has:
  - Created By
  - Updated By
  - Created At
  - Updated At
- Every important action generates an Activity Log.

